PROJECT DESCRIPTION - BENNET

OVERALL INTENTION:
An application that helps the user to cultivate healthy, life-supporting habbits, in an easy & natural way.


' GOAL - SETTING ' 
The user defines one+ goal(s) he has.
Then he chooses habbit(s) to work towards that goal on a daily basis.
AI will log the habbits of every user in one vector database,
to give the user recommendations / ideas for new habbits if desired.


' HABBIT - REFLECTION ' 
He chooses a convenient time / point in his routine where he logs his progress (daily).
He checks which habbits he completed and which not, 
and also logs wether it was easy or he struggled with it.

(If he found himself to struggle,
he can choose to talk to an 'AI-Habbit-Coach' that supports him in making 
small adjustment in his habbit or the way he approaches it, 
to make it more easy and natural.)*


' HABBIT - LOG '
The user has the ability at any time to see the progress he made in the past week
in a simple overview. 



